<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Login Alert</title>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>Login Alert</h1>
    <p>Hello <%= username %>,</p>

    <p>Your login information was recently accessed on <%= new Date(updatedAt).toLocaleString() %>. If you did not
            perform this action, please take appropriate security measures immediately.</p>

    <p>Here is the information about the login:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>User ID: <%= _id %>
        </li>
        <li>Username: <%= username %>
        </li>
        <li>Email: <%= email %>
        </li>
        <li>Timestamp of Login: <%= new Date(updatedAt).toLocaleString() %>
        </li>
    </ul>

    <p>If you have any concerns or questions regarding this login activity, please contact our support team.</p>

    <p>Thank you for using our service.</p>

    <p>Sincerely,<br>Your Website Team</p>
</body>

</html>
